
[00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000]  各位北村家,弟兄姊妹,堂慶蒙恩(Blessings to brothers and sisters of MPAC's family)
[00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:11.000]  各位弟兄跟我說生日快樂(There was a brother who said to me happy birthday)
[00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:16.000]  都是我們今天一齊的生日(It's actually birthday for all of us today)
[00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000]  今天我們一齊來到錦恩(Today we give thanks together)
[00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:26.000]  我都跟大家分享錦恩的事(And I want to share with you things of thanksgiving)
[00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:30.000]  去思想神的恩典(To think about the grace of God)
[00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:39.000]  也都去思想特別是神給我們的救恩(And to think especially about the salvation God has given us)
[00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:47.000]  很多時候弟兄姊妹都會自稱是蒙恩人(A lot of times you would say that we are those who have received grace or we are blessed)
[00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:55.000]  很多時候我們有弟兄姊妹奉獻在徵信錄裡面就自稱是蒙恩人(And often in our offering envelope)
[00:00:55.000 --> 00:00:58.000]  我們會說我們是神給的恩典(We put in we are blessed or we received grace)
[00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:05.000]  我們的身份就是蒙受恩典的人(And that is our status, we have received grace)
[00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:10.000]  我們是蒙受神恩典的人(We have received grace from God)
[00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:14.000]  一位年長的弟兄(There was an elderly brother)
[00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:17.000]  在他年長的時候(And when he was quite elderly)
[00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:20.000]  他講述自己一生(And he was talking about his life)
[00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:26.000]  講述了很多很多神給他的恩典(And he was talking about all the blessings and grace that God has given him throughout his life)
[00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:29.000]  然後他最後說(And then he said at last, at last)
[00:01:29.000 --> 00:01:32.000]  在這麼多經歷中(In all his experiences)
[00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:34.000]  我仍然覺得最大的恩典(I still feel the greatest grace)
[00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:38.000]  就是我信了耶穌(Is that I have believed Jesus)
[00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:44.000]  他領受了神給他永恆的生命(He received the eternal life from God)
[00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:48.000]  是最大的恩典(Is the greatest grace)
[00:01:48.000 --> 00:01:53.000]  當我們讀到聖經而忽所書的時候(When we read the Bible)
[00:01:53.000 --> 00:01:57.000]  講到神的恩典(When he was reading the book of Ephesians in the Bible)
[00:01:57.000 --> 00:01:59.000]  講到神的恩典(When he was reading the book of Ephesians in the Bible)
